-- China's Rare-Earths Restrictions Are in Line With WTO Rules, Ministry Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-15T03:06:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/china-s-rare-earths-restrictions-are-in-line-with-wto-rules-ministry-says.html
China’s restrictions on rare earth
exports and manufacturing are in line with World Trade
Organization policy, Yao Jian, spokesman for China’s Ministry of
Commerce, said today at a press conference in Beijing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
